ResourceInterface
public static enum ResourceInterface.State
extends java.lang.Enum<ResourceInterface.State>

The states are provided as a convenience. The resource may or may not implement them.

 NEW       : Instantiated but not initialized.

 RUNNING   : Active and healthy.

 UNHEALTHY : Active but not healthy.

 DISPOSING : Being disposed.

 DEAD      : Dead and gone.
